5. Neurodegenerative Disease Therapeutics:
   - Alzheimer's Disease: Aβ aggregation inhibitors, tau modulators, anti-inflammatory agents, cholinesterase inhibitors
   - Parkinson's Disease: L-DOPA, dopamine agonists, MAO-B inhibitors, α-synuclein aggregation inhibitors
